AC_PROG_CC
AC_PROG_CXX
AC_PROG_INSTALL
AC_PROG_LIBTOOL
AC_HEADER_STDC

dnl Checks for libraries.
dnl AC_CHECK_LIB(LIBRARY, FUNCT, [ACT-IF-FOUND], [ACT-IF-NOT])
